    <para os="ma">The following patch adds NPTL support:</para>

<screen os="mb"><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../&linux-libc-headers-mips_tls-patch;</userinput></screen>

    <para os="mc">The following patch fixes a compile issue with sysklogd:</para>

<screen os="md"><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../&linux-libc-headers-mips_atomic_fix-patch;</userinput></screen>

    <para os="me">Install the header files:</para>

<screen os="mf"><userinput>install -dv /usr/include/{asm,linux,mtd,scsi}
cp -arv include/asm-mips/* /usr/include/asm
cp -arv include/linux/* /usr/include/linux
cp -arv include/mtd/* /usr/include/mtd
cp -arv include/scsi/* /usr/include/scsi</userinput></screen>

